- Use exact phrasing except placeholders
- Replace <observationCount> with the exact integer from FACTS_JSON
- Replace {{timeWord}} with "time" if 1, "times" otherwise
- Use values from FACTS_JSON for {{expected}}, {{path}}, {{issue}} (or "missing")